text: Georgsdorf is a community in Bentheim in Lower Saxony. ==Geography== ===Place=== Georgsdorf is north of Nordhorn on the Süd-Nord-Kanal (South-North Canal) and the Coevorden-Piccardie-Kanal. It belongs to the Joint Community (Samtgemeinde) of Neuenhaus, whose administrative seat is in the like-named town. ==References== ==Other websites== * Georgsdorf’s webpage * Joint community’s webpage Category:County of Bentheim (district)
